  - `src/app/api/classes/[slug]/route.ts`: removed 5× `::bigint` casts (lecture/mcq/cq counts); FILTER kept; generics `bigint`→`number`.
  - `src/app/api/board-questions/route.ts`: removed 8× `::int` casts (analytics queries).
