  - `src/proxy.ts`: added `'/api/subjects'` to `PUBLIC_API_ROUTES` so public subject-detail GET (`SubjectHubPage.tsx:106`) is no longer 401'd. (No admin-only `/api/subjects` list route exists — only `[id]` — so widening is safe.)
- **Verified**: all anon navbar-destination endpoints now return 200 — `classes`, `classes/class-6` (was 500), `subjects/[id]` (was 401), `chapters/[id]` (was 500), `board-questions` (was 500), `courses?action=list`, `suggestions`, `notices`, `content-types`. `courses` needs `?action=list` (that was a 400 false-alarm from my test). `exam-center`/`premium` 401 = intended auth-gated.
- Lint clean on all changed files; tsc clean for changed files. Diagnostic file `diag-raw.mts` removed.

